data.text: @EBONYMag How come you don't have your own page?  I love Leslie Jones ❤️🖤💚😍
@EBONYMag I saw her on @TheView yesterday talking about just wanting to make people laugh so they will not be sad.  But when comedians make fun of rape, body shame people, death its not funny.

@EBONYMag Sorry @Lesdoggg but since comedians are now winning Oscars, getting nominated for Pulitzers, and breaking IQ tests, We kinda have to hold you all to a higher standard in your craft (on & off stage)
@EBONYMag Like it! We would like to invite you to read our comics. https://t.co/idfuN1GNBb

“ It’s comedy “ !!
